{"pageProps":{"post":{"_createdAt":"2022-06-21T11:16:57Z","_id":"0b9cd076-9bba-466c-9fa5-8b7034a4f07f","author":{"image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-339f8e320ddfad52225d31a181b162996e1c02d1-876x876-png","_type":"reference"}},"name":"üëæ Game Master"},"body":[{"_key":"4f320875eccc","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"69fd9e0136ae0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"What are Porter‚Äôs Five Forces?"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"c216bfb68221","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2a89b1e5ef0a0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Porter‚Äôs five forces is a fundamental, qualitative valuation framework to help evaluate an industry‚Äôs strengths and weaknesses through five competitive forces. It can also be applied to evaluate companies. "},{"_key":"2a89b1e5ef0a1","_type":"span","marks":["em"],"text":"The model is first developed by the Harvard Business School professor, Michael E. Porter in his book \"Competitive Strategy: Techniques for Analyzing Industries and Competitors‚Äù."},{"_key":"2a89b1e5ef0a2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" The five forces are:"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"45f0a2682c22","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"49bb2b2235b60","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The threat of substitute products"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0270b4fbf9de","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e87ad729b0400","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The threat of new entrant"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"314eabd128c8","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"9889208575d70","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Bargaining power of suppliers"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"e4ea3ca88ac0","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"deee9c7bc5320","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Bargaining power of buyers"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"97bf138c72a0","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"edffd67511120","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Industry rivalry"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"91154592caa0","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f4df645dfb570","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"It is worth noticing that the difference between ‚Äúthreat of substitute products‚Äù and ‚Äúindustry rivalry‚Äù can be tricky for new investors. The threat of substitute products represents products from another industry that can offer a similar benefit and user experience as the product produced by the companies within a selected industry. On the other hand, industry rivalry represents the direct competition within the selected industry."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"ca722a5b97d4","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"95f848537cc9","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"1cca1a9fe3b2","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-ff9438a805813e56ee84a99f4216eb2b1917f8c1-1361x765-png","_type":"reference"}},{"_key":"a0ed9943b545","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"34c04e4c1ca90","_type":"span","marks":["em"],"text":"Graph source: "},{"_key":"34c04e4c1ca91","_type":"span","marks":["47525846a083","em"],"text":"https://www.business-to-you.com/porters-five-forces/"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"47525846a083","_type":"link","href":"https://www.business-to-you.com/porters-five-forces/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"a8be6c4e5787","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"b51202e000960","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Ideally, when the five forces are weak, a company has gained greater power to charge its customers a higher price to achieve more profits, creating a monopoly. When the forces are strong, the companies are forced to join the ‚Äúprice war‚Äù and lower its price to attract more customers. In this case, the industry will turn into a perfect competition market, with high rivalries."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"comments":[],"description":"Classical business framework.","mainImage":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-e7ab357d223a51b853ccc57072f5e5834a232953-1024x576-jpg","_type":"reference"}},"slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"porter-s-five-forces"},"title":"Porter's Five Forces"}},"__N_SSG":true}